      "text": "このコーナーでは様々なアイドルがリスナーさんの\nお悩みに答えていきます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In this section‚ various idols will answer listeners' concerns\nUp until now‚ it seems that many idols showed",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_03-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "今までのアイドルはひとクセある方が多かった\nようですが、私なりに頑張らせていただきますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "their quirks so far‚\nbut I'll do my best in my own way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.1333333333
    },
