      "text": "（本来なら明るく突飛な答えを言いそうな）\n（芽衣にお願いしたいところだが……どうなるか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Normally‚ I'd usually leave it to Mei who would give brighy and）\n（straight answer. but… let's see what happens.）",
