    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_03-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "「高校生です。部活で疲れてしまい、帰宅後はコーヒー\nを飲んで夜中まで勉強して、休日は寝だめしています」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"I'm a high school student. After club activities‚ I drink coffee‚\nstudy until midnight‚ and catch up on sleep on weekends.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_03-ski019.m4a",
      "text": "「沙季さんは生徒会長もされてるとのことですが、\nアイドルと学校生活をどう両立させているんですか？」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Saki-san is also the student council president‚\nso how do you manage being an idol and school life?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 167.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_03-ski020.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……それではまず、ご自分の生活に合った\n勉強スタイルを見つけてみてはどうでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… First‚ why don't you try finding a study style that\nsuits your lifestyle?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 175.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
