      "text": "早起きが出来るのであれば、学校に行く前の一時間を\n勉強時間に充ててもいいですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you can wake up early‚ you can allocate an hour\nbefore school for studying.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_03-ski022.m4a",
      "text": "部活を終えて帰宅する前にどこかに寄って\n気持ちがオフになる前に勉強するのも手ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Or you could stop by somewhere to study on your way home\nfrom club before you get too tired.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 189
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
