      "text": "それと、カフェインは寝る六時間前までで摂取を\nやめた方が睡眠の質は良くなります。他にも――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ it's better for the quality of your sleep to stop caffeine\nintake at least six hours before bedtime. Besides――",
        "id": ""
