      "text": "凄いな……ここまで本気の回答をするとは\nスタッフさんも驚いてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Impressive… I didn't expect such a serious response.\nEven the staff seems surprised.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 205.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_03-ski024.m4a",
      "text": "私は朝型ですが、芽衣ちゃんやすずちゃん、怜ちゃん\n辺りは夜型ですね。いつも朝はむにゃむにゃしています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm a morning person‚ but Mei-chan‚ Suzu-chan‚ and Rei-chan\nare night owls. They're always groggy in the mornings.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_04_03-ski025.m4a",
      "text": "学生生活は大変だと思いますが\n頑張った分だけ達成感も大きいと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think student life is tough‚ but\nI believe the sense of achievement is greater with the effort.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 219.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 222.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
